TestLlmQueryWithSchemaAnnotatesDownstreamAsJson
/ llm.query.Build() returns "json" when a Schema parameter is set.
/ Downstream snapshot must read %y%(json), not (object) — the typed
/ schema contract flows through Build() into the .pr Type stamp.
- builder.goals from 'probes/llm/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- set %annot% = %snapshot[1].y%
- assert.equals expected='item', actual=%annot%
